{'id': 38879677, 'body': "Hi Tifani, thank you for sharing this feedback with us. We're so glad to hear how much your kids love Pok Pok. 

A play-lock actually exists on all Apple devices, it's called GUIDED ACCESS. To set it up, go to Settings > Accessibility, then turn on Guided Access. This way your child won't be able to exit Pok Pok while they're playingâ€”we know how quickly that can happen!
", 'modified': '2023-09-12T20:00:31Z'}

{'id': 38855609, 'body': 'Thank you Sierra, this is amazing feedback. We're actually already thinking about #1 and how we can customize the playroom area so parents can do toy rotations in the app. 

Your second suggestion is particularly interesting. We actually have zero language in the app at all. The language the characters are "speaking" is actually not a language at all, but  gibberish. We do this so that kids can create their own narrative and tell stories however they choose. It also enables the stories to be different every time, so each play session is totally unique and open-ended.\xa0

This also ensures that kids growing up multi-lingual aren't pigeonholed into just one language, but can interpret the Pok Pok gibberish as neutral and add their own language on top when they play with the storytelling toys like Town, House and Islands.', 'modified': '2023-09-11T18:42:55Z'}

{'id': 23025463, 'body': "Thanks aquateenhungerfan, this is really valuable feedback that we'll definitely keep in mind as we continue to update the Playroom. We can understand why some folks prefer one-time payments, but the reason we chose a subscription for the Playroom is so that we can continue to develop both new toys and expand existing toys for kids over time. Also, we love that kids don't ever have to get stuck by a paywall while they're playing.

It's really wonderful to hear that you can see all of the passion and hard work that we dedicated to the Playroomâ€”we're really glad that came through, even if the subscription might not be for you. 

Thanks again!", 'modified': '2021-05-26T14:04:06Z'}

